  "text": "The idea here is intelligent gathering while protecting live environment, and ultimately paralysing the Trojan botnet. With the utilisation of virtual machines or cloud based simulation platforms security experts can gather sufficient evidence up to successful prosecution provided the integrity of the evidence is accounted for [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] . With offensive strategies skiing on the edge of the line of legality and ethics, one needs to be very careful as attacking back is not only unethical but illegal too.",
